  "synopsis": "Doom came to Shin Young-jun, a cook sergeant, just a few days before his final vacation. The battalion turned into chaos in an instant, and the communication network was cut off. There is only one thing visible before your eyes! \\[Congratulations on your awakening!\\] \\[Job: New Chef Lv.1\\] If I had been a warrior or an assassin, I would have tried to stand alone... What was given to him was a chef, which is obviously a support job. There's nothing I can do when it's like this. 'From now on, I will feed you.' \n\n(Source: Naver, translated)",
